dotCloud, use Perl;

A Perl Mongers talk on using dotCloud with Perl.

Examples given using Mojolicious web framework.

Presented to Thousand Oaks Perl Mongers 8/9/2012.

David Oswald

daoswald@gmail.com
davido@cpan.org

